Bringing an upgrade to a Formula One car is far from straightforward… each component, no matter how big or small, requires many different steps to design, test, produce and hit the track 🛠️

So, how do F1 teams develop their cars? John, Mike and Lewis explain! 👀

node.title: How Do Teams Develop a Formula One Car?
